on Linux servers.

12
00:00:23,449 --> 00:00:26,609
Now, compared to using a
graphical environment, or GUI,

13
00:00:26,609 --> 00:00:28,439
when you use the
shell, you do have

14
00:00:28,440 --> 00:00:31,230
to remember a bunch of magic
words and incantations.

15
00:00:31,230 --> 00:00:33,660
But in exchange, once
you get some practice in,

16
00:00:33,659 --> 00:00:35,219
you get to do things
really quickly

17
00:00:35,219 --> 00:00:37,049
without a lot of
pointing and clicking.

18
00:00:37,049 --> 00:00:39,539
