line is pretty much the same.

22
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:50,460
You type out instructions
in a special language,

23
00:00:50,460 --> 00:00:51,630
and the system runs them.

24
00:00:51,630 --> 00:00:53,504
And it shows you the
output underneath.

25
00:00:53,503 --> 00:00:54,669
Then you get another prompt.

26
00:00:54,670 --> 00:00:56,130
And you can do it again.

27
00:00:56,130 --> 00:00:58,950
